{"type":"assistant","message":{"content":[{"text":"F-017 is complete. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Feature Status: COMPLETE** — all work committed to `dev/F-017-1774176172`\n\n**What existed (already implemented):**\n- `/config` command handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/config.js`) — list/get/set/reset subcommands\n- `configService` (`src/services/config-service.js`) — runtime config with safe-key whitelist and sensitive masking\n- Registration in `telegram.js` (line 511) and `permission-guard.js` (admin-only)\n\n**Bug fixed:**\n- `configService.resetConfig()` failed when env vars were set after module import — fixed by lazy-capturing `originalEnvValues` at first `setConfig` call instead of only at module init\n\n**Tests: 32/32 passing** (18 service + 14 handler)\n\n**All acceptance criteria met:**\n- ✅ `/config` lists all config with `***` masking for sensitive fields\n- ✅ `/config get <KEY>` returns current value\n- ✅ `/config set <KEY>=<VALUE>` modifies safe keys, immediately effective\n- ✅ Sensitive keys (TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN etc) blocked from set\n- ✅ Admin-only via F-006 `isAdmin()` check\n- ✅ `/config reset <KEY>` restores to original `.env` value","type":"text"}],"id":"req_vrtx_011CZHzkoccpKFNM4aF9CFbg","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":838,"output_tokens":1,"cache_read_input_tokens":81360},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e46239e5-8540-42b3-8b45-910022f21a71","uuid":"e5d6f648-b9ea-4681-8d10-b3e6818189a2"}
